headline: 4 Security & Safety Stocks Poised to Gain on Promising Industry Trends
summary: The Zacks Security and Safety Services industry has been gaining from growing awareness for safety and security among people. ALLE, LIF, ALRM and CDRE are some notable stocks in the industry.
